🎤 Introducing Our First Host: @theivyrivera 🎤

Brooklyn's own Ivy Rivera is rewriting the book on "hustle." With a dynamic background as a Media Personality and Record Label Executive, Ivy brings over five years of experience in amplifying brand presence across multiple markets. Her journey is a testament to her passion for inclusion, empowerment, and success.

From ruling the airwaves at Brooklyn College radio to making her mark at Power 105.1 in New York, Ivy's journey is nothing short of inspiring. Her influence extends far beyond the mic, as she's also renowned for her marketing expertise in brand architecture, campaigns, social media, digital strategies, PR, and influencer collaborations.

Join us as Ivy Rivera takes the stage, bringing her charisma, insights, and passion for empowerment to the BLACK STYLE X NYFW PANEL & SHOWCASE event. Get ready to be inspired by her remarkable journey and invaluable contributions to the industry. 🌟 #BlackStyleX
